data.description:
Now offering $5,000 in Seller Concessions to qualified offers! All the space you need in this two level, five bedroom home in Highlands East. Enter this home to vaulted ceilings, living room, large formal dining room with wood burning fireplace and large kitchen with tons of storage. The kitchen has new refrigerator and dishwasher, large farmhouse sink, and a hutch being left for the next owners. Two bedrooms and full bathroom on main level, including the primary bedroom with private full bath. Two more bedrooms, bathroom, living room, and laundry room can be found in the finished basement. 

The home has areas of fresh paint, new water heater in 2020, kitchen flooring installed in 2021, operable wood burning fireplace upstairs, chimney and fire insert for wood burning fireplace downstairs, humidifier built in the furnace, and central air.
